Dialogs.Dialog: Well... ▲高嶺＊＊▲. What do you think about kissing？
No, I mean... Well, it's like... You might not quite like it or something...
That's what I used to think... But lately, it's different.
I feel relieved whenever you kiss me... I'm kidding.
▲高嶺＊＊▲... I'm glad. Then I'll be more confident and do it more--
Geez, don't get ahead of yourself. No！
Well... ▲高嶺＊＊▲. What do you think about kissing？
I've been thinking about what I should do if you didn't like it...
How can I not like it when you kiss me？ No, I want more...
...Sorry. I didn't hear it clearly. Can you say it again？
With that face... You heard it clearly, no？
(When she makes that face, I can't possibly tease her anymore.)
Well... ▲高嶺＊＊▲. What do you think about kissing？
As long as the only one you kiss is me, that's fine.
When the one I love... I mean, when you feel like you want to touch me, I feel the same too.
...That's probably enough for my answer, right？
Well... ▲高嶺＊＊▲. What do you think about kissing？
No, I'm just a little concerned.
So, it's not something you can just be "a little" concerned about, okay...？
I-I'm so sorry. But, for example...
▲主人公＊▲. Can I ask you a question？
Um... When you kiss me, do you feel nervous？
！？ W-Well... All the time, I guess.
I see... Then how about our first time？
My heart was throbbing like crazy... But why did you bring up this topic, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Um... I just wondered what I have to do if I want to initiate...
Hmm... Does this mean that ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is going to kiss me？
Eh？ F-For real, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？ Are you going to？
▲主人公＊▲. Can I ask you a question？
▲主人公＊▲. Do you know how many kinds of kisses there are？
W-What！？ W-Why did you ask me that, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！？
Not really weird. It's just shocking...
I just think that if I do research beforehand, it might help in the actual situation...
...I'm glad. I'm still not ready yet, so you have to wait, okay？
▲主人公＊▲. Can I ask you a question？
Hmm... I know！ You want a kiss！
Eh！？ Really！？ Yay！ Here comes my reward...
(I'll have to be careful next time...)
▲高嶺＊＊▲. What do you think about love？
"Life is infinitely stranger than anything which the mind of man could invent."
Just replace "life" with "love" in that quote, and it will still be true.
Love is strange, and mysterious...But I do know one thing.
...No, the more I know, the less I understand. It's so mysterious.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. What do you think about love？
Hmm, both unrequited love and mutual love are just love, right？ It's painful. It's miserable. But it's also enjoyable.
Even so, I still want to be with you. It's that powerful, I guess.
▲高嶺＊＊▲ has given me more than enough. How about you then, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
...Yes. Now, I also have my power. Thank you.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. What do you think about love？
If I had never known what love is, maybe I would have never had the feelings of jealousy and envy...
...Yeah. Honestly, that's what I've been thinking.
But, even then... No, you've taught me a lot more than that. So, never leave me, okay？
It's my first time learning these things, so I might become lost.
So, you have to take care of me and never leave me, okay？
▲高嶺＊＊▲. What would your ideal situation be if someone confessed his love to you？
Well, I just kind of wondered.
Maybe like a happy ending scene where the prince comes to take me.
(As I thought, ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is such an innocent girl...)
...I know though, that reality and fairy tales are different, okay？
(Urgh. As if she knows what I'm thinking...)
▲高嶺＊＊▲. What do you think about love？ Can you solve its mystery？
Well... Love is complicated and difficult. It can also be confusing...
But whenever I'm with you, I don't think about these things anymore.
I don't know why. I don't think I can ever solve this mystery, but...
iWhen I see you, I can feel your warmth and your sweetness... I think these are more than enough... Yeah.
No. Why am I saying such things？
▲高嶺＊＊▲. What do you think about love？
Hm... For human beings... No, for me, I'm quite aware that it's greed, I think.
Yes. I get all the power, but it never seems to be enough.
Love is scary. I feel like I am becoming an ugly person......
...I see. But it's all because ▲高嶺＊＊▲ loves me, right？
Not at all. Come on. Be confident！
Thank you... I'm glad I love you.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. What do you think about love？
Well, I think it's something I shouldn't think about too much... I guess.
Something you shouldn't think about too much？
Yeah. Since it's my first time, it would be natural for me to feel troubled or lost.
...But if I have you as my stable goal, everything will be just fine, right？
But sometimes, I'll feel insecure. During those times, I'll be fine if you just hold my hands, okay？
▲高嶺＊＊▲, when do you feel jealous？
Because I'm your girlfriend. I trust you.
But, not even a little bit？
...Are you saying that you did something that would make me feel jealous？
Ah, no！ I would never do something like that！
(Ah... Why did I ask such a suspicious question！？)
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Do you think you are the jealous type？
To what extent...？ Want to try？
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Do you think you are the jealous type？
Because it's horrible. I can't stand it if you get close to other girls.
Takane Manaka will be full of jealousy at a time like that！ I'm kidding...
(▲高嶺＊＊▲ will be full of jealousy...？ I wonder what that would be like...)
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Do you think you are the jealous type？
Let me think... I don't think so.
I see... So you've never been jealous before？
Yeah... Usually I'm the one that others feel jealous of...
I wonder why people get jealous of an ordinary girl like me. Do you know why？
(▲高嶺＊＊▲ probably doesn't realize how perfect she is from other's point of view...)
▲高嶺＊＊▲, when do you feel jealous？
What's with that expression？ Do you still have doubts in me！？
...Do you really want me to be jealous？ Fine！
I'm so jealous that I want to lock you up somewhere so that you can never lay your eyes on anyone else.
...So you are into that kind of stuff？
I didn't mean it like that...！
(This kind of joke is too much then...)
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Do you think you are the jealous type？
I see. Do you imagine things by yourself and cry, or something like that？
Hey, how can I tell you that？ ...Do you hate jealous girls？
Hmm... If they're jealous in a cute way, I think that's okay.
...I absolutely can't let you get close to other girls.
(I think she gets jealous like that sometimes...)
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Do you think you are the jealous type？
You asked me this before. Well, my answer is still the same.
It's difficult for me since I have such a wonderful boyfriend. Oh well...
Hey, you get easily carried away. Hehe▼
(Yeah, things are fine the way they are！)
What do you think about skinship？
Hmm... I don't quite like it.
It's not that I really don't like it. I just... How should I say it？ It depends on the intention...
...Hmm？ You do have some self-awareness. Pervert.
What do you think about skinship？
It's not that I hate it. But... sometimes I get startled if it's sudden.
R-Really？ That happened, huh？ I'm sorry. From now on, I'll...
But, if you announce what you intend to do and then touch me recklessly, that would be embarrassing as well.
Ah, sorry. Were you about to say something？
What do you think about skinship？
Urgh... Don't tell me you hate it.
No, for something like that, it's more about TPO...
TPO... You mean time, place... And what is the last one？
...What can it be？ Um, it must start with "o"...
Opportunity...？ Like the name of Mars Exploration Rover？ No... Ah, it must be occasion！
Ah, right！ Hehe, now I remember it.
(Yeah, I got it right！ ...Eh？ What were we talking about earlier？)
What do you think about skinship？ I mean in cases of skinship between opposite genders...
If they are dating, I guess it's okay at some point.
Like starting from holding hands, and then hugging...
Originally, the term "skinship" was used only for physical contact between parents and children, no？
What do you think about skinship？
I think I like it more than before... Well, I don't think it's bad.
Is it something to be that happy about？
Of course！ It means my skinship is getting better and better！
Geez, you're getting ahead of yourself.
But, um... I'm starting to understand that physical contact is an important thing.
Don't be too enthusiastic about it, okay？ I'm not very good with things like this.
(Urgh... I've got to be careful... But... Hooray！！)
What do you think about skinship？
Well, for something like that, the most important thing is timing.
Yeah, like if I feel like holding hands, and then you suddenly hold my hand.
Things like that make me feel as if we understand each other's feelings, and I feel happy... Yeah.
Hey, don't look at me like that. I feel embarrassed.
What do you think about skinship？
We've talked about this before, no？ Hmm...
Yeah, but I want you to give me your input again.
I think you've followed the TPO rule quite well.
Hehe, full score▼ But, don't get ahead of yourself because of it, okay？
